# The agent saves generated deliverables here:
#   content/    – social post copy, content calendars
#   campaigns/  – one folder per campaign (plan, KOL briefs, ad build-sheets)
#   analytics/  – monthly reports, UTM convention + log, competitor scans
#   assets/     – creative briefs + links to creative files
# These subfolders are created on demand. Generated work IS committed (so it syncs A<->B);
# big binaries are not — link them from analytics/ or assets/ instead.
